results.full_text: Dear Joan, I would like to take a moment to say THANK YOU for saving me about $16,000!!! Your program allowed me to advertise my home on the MLS website. Within 24 hours of being activated, I had more phone calls than I could have ever hoped for and had a deal within days. This program is the answer to selling by owner!!! You were ALWAYS available to answer any questions and there were NO strings attached. Thank you, again, for your assistance and a FANTASTIC program! I would recommend this (and have…numerous times already) to ANYONE trying to sell their houses “For Sale By Owner!”Michelle – Strongsville Ohio
